<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Redstone</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">With a population of a mere 824 inhabitants, the Redstone Real Estate offers a variety of housing options complete with large garages and verandas.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Focused around the concepts of healthy and sustainable family living, the community in Redstone perfectly blends suburban minimalism with modern conveniences to offer its residents the best of both worlds.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood is an ideal settlement option for individuals who prefer leading a tranquil life, tucked away from the maddening bustle of the city.</p>
